    "As shown in Table 3, y DRG_base ∈ {0, 1, …, 339} and y CC ∈ {0, …, 4}, representing the categories of [\"without CC/MCC\", \"with CC\", \"with MCC\", \"without MCC\", and \"not applicable\"] respectively.",
